467fcdf7258","tid":1863560,"uid":176121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"試下排隊時叫口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776b6c4232c886028abd0fc3665a4844378c0adf","tid":1863560,"uid":73143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"[全民三罷] 醫護工會並不代表所有 醫護，以及 香港人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eQoLAS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eQoLAS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>上醫醫國，中醫醫人，下醫醫病</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n鑑於太多吹風唔罷<br />\n我想講既係醫護罷工起左個頭後，好多工會都準備緊<br />\n香港人要做既係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全港大三罷</span></span></strong><br />\n直至政府做返本身佢應該要做既事，甚至係五大訴求<br />\n成個制度已經由內至外腐爛，一日唔改變都只會有同樣既事情發生<br />\n而唔係咩社區大爆發之後成班返去醫院醫病<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醫護工會並不代表所有醫護，以及 香港人<br />\n<br />\n妥協只會失敗</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzWp8d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzWp8d0.png&h=12ec3a53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b10a3fae094195dd62d07cc39b7d74d32a5d0ce9","tid":1863560,"uid":180719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:40:44.000Z","msg":"九龍灣仲癲"}]}